{"tid":1287370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"杜汶澤兩度淚崩直播尋企圖輕生者　「我去搵緊你，係都見埋我先」","createTime":"2019-07-05T07:37:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T07:38:47.000Z","uid":68738,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"860d5e4d4d1180891c3217b9390d7bb7e0044d8b","tid":1287370,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2994809/org/a18de9f0e1d393c5e4d69250498a2962.jpg/yBp6RH7gjfonRaJMuUvLxmKrJB1H2RBj9ymPOfcpjzk?v=w960r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2994809%2Forg%2Fa18de9f0e1d393c5e4d69250498a2962.jpg%2FyBp6RH7gjfonRaJMuUvLxmKrJB1H2RBj9ymPOfcpjzk%3Fv%3Dw960r16_9&h=8f0a0665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2994532/org/51a0b57856e19102dc3ec56842b2256a.jpg/bB02BzI2OXI7akhJc-SAIXGpNEVjKFF4pvOOaabzjmk?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2994532%2Forg%2F51a0b57856e19102dc3ec56842b2256a.jpg%2FbB02BzI2OXI7akhJc-SAIXGpNEVjKFF4pvOOaabzjmk%3Fv%3Dw960&h=7767a7a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"184754edc9cb8d72931eb6b03282b7ec42fae608","tid":1287370,"uid":68738,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:38:25.000Z","msg":"杜汶澤一直都有關汪「逃犯條例」，他今日得知有人再想犧牲生命時，在Facebook進行呼籲，好讓大家幫忙尋人「啱啱同事send 比我，有一名豬友響Facebook post 咗話要自殺。喇XXX你唔好死住，係都見埋我先！你響邊度，我send咗Whatsapp 比你，Check 下！我依家出去搵你！大家都留意下：銀色Toyota Echo見到打比 XXX」而在08:44am再度更新「已經聯絡到佢個friend，去緊同佢個friend一齊搵佢。」<br />\n<br />\n杜汶澤一知道他有此念頭後，馬上出車在聯和墟尋人，他更含淚拍片：「喇！啊XXX我依家見到你仲online嘅，但我喺聯和墟周圍兜我搵你唔到啊，喂你可唔可以話俾我聽你喺邊到呢？兄弟你唔好放棄啊！我去搵緊你啊OK？」<br />\n短時間後，杜汶澤再上傳一段片段，今次阿澤真係感到好心痛，更喊晒口：「咁多香港人都冇放棄，你唔可以隨便放棄啊，XXX你知唔知啊？你覆我Whatsapp啦好冇啊？」講到此時阿澤已經淚落滿面，而太太田蕊妮更有留言「XXX求下你覆佢WhatsApp pls ! 杜汶澤你要小心揸車！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2994518/org/94f4fef033c327d87cfaaa67a1857f81.jpg/0oF6rdEap-NpQXUCPQQf9yMGVTbQKirHtpWqYbaVqmE?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2994518%2Forg%2F94f4fef033c327d87cfaaa67a1857f81.jpg%2F0oF6rdEap-NpQXUCPQQf9yMGVTbQKirHtpWqYbaVqmE%3Fv%3Dw960&h=d0d3fb7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後過多1個小時，杜汶澤上傳一張救護車照片寫下「搵到喇！白車檢查中。」不少網民都留言寫下「Thank you」、「謝謝杜生」、「辛苦了」、「一個都不能少」等等留言，今次真的幸好找回他且救回一條人命。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2995207/org/76f75376532791a4d1c8e1d0867c3e6e.jpg/8-JC1kHGpFXJ4bVPbOLGV11LYOXe62i8btVmlW7VZpU?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2995207%2Forg%2F76f75376532791a4d1c8e1d0867c3e6e.jpg%2F8-JC1kHGpFXJ4bVPbOLGV11LYOXe62i8btVmlW7VZpU%3Fv%3Dw960&h=7f4d6c95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"403493a5992262b026874c0d4d99687b5d8436e1","tid":1287370,"uid":155431,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:38:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔睇01</span></span>"}]}